Hello guys, you might not know me but i was the creater of Funscap3 and i quit coding and the server about 3 years ago or more i dont remember but my server was Funscap3. A all pking base server that is a lot of fun even though its a bit unstable i worked hours on it, this is unlike most servers today this is the old style private servers where you mass objects to get xp :) Ill post some old pics i have from years ago. Also i don't remember if this was the last version i made because my computer crashed and i found the last uploaded. So enjoy. Please don't flame saying YOUR NOT THE CREATER because you are a dumb fuck if you do. By the way my Name is Justin. And this server has had over 20k+ downloads so :) i would love to host again but i cant
EDIT:If anyone is going to host this tell me because i can't host anymore and i would love to play.
For the compiler problems please right click on the compiler click "Edit" delete everything in there then pase this in" [code]@echo off @TITLE Funscap3 if exist "%programfiles%\Java" (call :compile "%programfiles%\Java\") else (goto error) :compile for /D %%x in ("%~1jdk*") do (set p="%%~x\bin\javac.exe") if defined p (%p% -cp . *.java) if defined p (goto end) :error echo You do not have Java installed. Please download it at the site that is about to load. :end echo press any key to continue... pause exit[/code]
